               <head>Genesis and Exodus</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/n85305131" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>Genesis and Exodus with Targum Onḳelos and Sa'adyah Ga'on's Arabic translation, with Hebrew grammar Maḥberet al-tigan (מחברת אלתיגאן) at the beginning of the manuscript.</summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he" otherLangs="tmr-Hebr jrb-Hebr">Hebrew, Aramaic, Judeo-Arabic</textLang>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem n="0" rend="visible" class="lccn.loc.gov/n85305131">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1v" to="234r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Bereshit u-shemot </title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">בראשית ושמות</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <textLang mainLang="he" otherLangs="tmr-Hebr jrb-Hebr">Hebrew, Aramaic, Judeo-Arabic</textLang>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The books of Genesis and Exodus accompanied by the Targum of Onḳelos and Sa'adyah's Arabic translation and preceded by the Maḥberet al-tigan.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The Hebrew text is provided with the ordinary vowel-signs and accents, while the Targum has the simple superlinear punctuation. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Some text has  been blacked out on folio 22v.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <colophon xml:lang="he">יזכה הכותב והנכתב לו לחזות ביו"ב(?) נשלם יום ה' ב' יומין מרחשון <date when="1425" calendar="Hebrew">ק'פ'ו'</date>
                        
                        
                        
                        <locus n="22r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     </colophon>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
                  
                  
                  
